       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COM89800.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COM89800.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     VIA Controlo Orçamental Detalhe                            *
      ******************************************************************
